>>REGINA: Doesn't
mean we should.

00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:58.183 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: Doesn't
mean that we should.

00:00:58.183 --> 00:01:01.225 align:middle line:84%
The technology has advanced
faster than our value.

00:01:01.225 --> 00:01:02.100 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:01:02.100 --> 00:01:03.350 align:middle line:90%
>>BRADEN: But I'm an optimist.

00:01:03.350 --> 00:01:04.430 align:middle line:90%
