>>BRADEN: It's been longer
than two years, I know.

00:01:53.310 --> 00:01:54.960 align:middle line:10%
And I'm really excited
to be with you,

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:58.710 align:middle line:10%
to be with your community,
with our community today.

00:01:58.710 --> 00:02:01.800 align:middle line:10%
Because this is just
such a precious time

00:02:01.800 --> 00:02:03.210 align:middle line:10%
in the history of our world.

00:02:03.210 --> 00:02:03.360 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Precious.

00:02:03.360 --> 00:02:04.530 align:middle line:10%
>>BRADEN: And it's a tough time.

00:02:04.530 --> 00:02:05.905 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's a
very tough time.

00:02:05.905 --> 00:02:08.610 align:middle line:84%
And a lot of times, we want to
avoid it and kind of put salve

00:02:08.610 --> 00:02:09.990 align:middle line:90%
