our very existence.

00:46:29.760 --> 00:46:31.530 align:middle line:90%
It threatens our species.

00:46:31.530 --> 00:46:34.930 align:middle line:84%
We'll never lose the
tech, but how we apply

00:46:34.930 --> 00:46:37.620 align:middle line:84%
it will be that
pendulum coming back.

00:46:37.620 --> 00:46:39.600 align:middle line:84%
We are maturing in
the common sense,

00:46:39.600 --> 00:46:42.210 align:middle line:84%
hopefully, of what
it means to be human

00:46:42.210 --> 00:46:44.360 align:middle line:84%
and how we embrace the
technology in our lives.

00:46:44.360 --> 00:46:45.235 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:46:45.235 --> 00:46:45.560 align:middle line:90%
Gregg--

00:46:45.560 --> 00:46:47.640 align:middle line:84%
>>BRADEN: And that's what the
new human story is all about.

00:46:47.640 --> 00:46:48.440 align:middle line:90%
